<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="еҲӣе»әзү№е®ҡж•°жҚ®">еҲӣе»әзү№е®ҡж•°жҚ®
  <a href="/tutorials/data-manipulation/np-pd/2-2-np-array/#еҲӣе»әзү№е®ҡж•°жҚ®" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
