<p>еҲӣе»әе…ЁдёҖж•°з»„, еҗҢж—¶д№ҹиғҪжҢҮе®ҡиҝҷдәӣзү№е®ҡж•°жҚ®зҡ„ <code class="highlighter-rouge">dtype</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ones</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">),</span><span class="n">dtype</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">)</span>   <span class="c1"># ж•°жҚ®дёә1пјҢ3иЎҢ4еҲ—
